      "es": "",
      "en": "Create a C runtime file descriptor from the file handle handle. The flags parameter should be a bitwise OR of os.O_APPEND, os.O_RDONLY, os.O_TEXT and os.O_NOINHERIT. The returned file descriptor may be used as a parameter to os.fdopen() to create a file object. The file descriptor is inheritable by default. Pass os.O_NOINHERIT flag to make it non inheritable. Raises an auditing event msvcrt.open_osfhandle with arguments handle, flags."
